                    <h4>Welcome to AccWeather!</h4>
                    <p>AccWeather is a comprehensive weather application designed to provide you with the most accurate and up-to-date weather information. Our mission is to help you stay informed about the weather conditions in your area so you can plan your activities accordingly.</p>
                    
                    <h4>Our Features</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Real-time Weather Updates:</strong> Get current weather conditions for any location around the world.</li>
                        <li><strong>Accurate Forecasts:</strong> View hourly and daily weather forecasts to help you plan ahead.</li>
                        <li><strong>Interactive Maps:</strong> Explore weather maps to track weather patterns and changes.</li>
                        <li><strong>Customizable Alerts:</strong> Set up alerts for severe weather conditions and stay safe.</li>
                        <li><strong>Historical Data:</strong> Access past weather data for research and planning purposes.</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>Meet the Team</h4>
                    <p>Our team is passionate about weather and technology. We strive to deliver a user-friendly and reliable weather application. If you have any questions or feedback, feel free to <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
                    
                    <h4>Our Story</h4>
                    <p>AccWeather was founded with the goal of creating a weather application that provides accurate and timely weather information to users worldwide. We are continuously working to improve our services and add new features to enhance your experience.</p>
                    
                    <h4>Contact Us</h4>
                    <p>If you have any questions, suggestions, or need support, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@accweather.com">support@accweather.com</a>.</p>
